Here's a look inside Virgin Galactic's spaceship that will fly tourists to space for about $250,000 a ticket.

@RachCrane talks to CEO Michael Colglazier and Chief Space Officer George Whitesides about designing a cabin for first-time astronauts. https://t.co/pgtrJi96kc https://t.co/1HzCIbIsNu

name: CNN
text: Researchers from MIT and Brigham and Women's Hospital in Boston have developed the iMASC, a new silicone mask that can be safely reused without fear of contamination. Researchers still need to analyze how effectively it catches viral particles https://t.co/zspXmkNYnc
